# Deploy after changes

After completing substantive code edits (features, fixes, refactors that affect runtime), run a production deploy so the live site stays in sync:

1. Run `npm run build` and fix any failures before deploying.
2. From the repo root: `npx vercel deploy --prod --yes`

Skip deploy only when the user explicitly says not to deploy or when changes are documentation-only with no effect on the app.
